I couldn’t think of a better tattoo to represent that trip and everything it encapsulates. Thank you so much @alexandra.nevares for lending your extraordinary talents and bringing our ideas to life. 🤩
I love them so much! 🥰

Manuel, 
Being with you has not only been the greatest adventure of my life thus far, it has been nothing short of a blessing. Sometimes I have to pinch myself because I find myself in the relationship, me being the hopeless romantic that I am, that I’ve always dreamt of. You truly are my person, my soulmate, and my best friend. Thank you so much for loving me, for pushing me to be my best self, and for working through every obstacle that we’ve had to face with such empathy and grace. You truly are an enigma and I am both forever in awe of you and eternally grateful for you. Happy 6 YEAR ANNIVERSARY my love, I can’t wait to marry you in 10 months! Here’s to you, here’s to us, and here’s too many many more! 🥹🥰❤️ #AO 👨‍❤️‍💋‍👨
